description: Beauty of the Bistro is a Kansas City food truck offering house made dishes with a twist and decadent desserts from scratch.Come to the Roaming ‘Carte du Jour’ on a street near you!Whether you meet us on the streets, or choose to hire us for a private catered event, we know you will appreciate every dish prepared, as it is inspired by an appreciation for fresh, local ingredients.
name: Beauty of the Bistro
